I've been playing for a while. Let's talk about the game Advantages: the game is novel, and the 2D stick figure combat mode is adopted Funny physical system, you can even kowtow Rich in weapons, every weapon can be fun Disadvantages: The server is rather bad, and there are often firewall errors when playing with friends building rooms. Obviously, the firewall is not opened I don't know if it's a problem that no one plays in Chinese clothes. I can't match people quickly during most of the working days, only people play at night There are also BUG problems, sometimes such as invincible, sudden disappearance of maps and so on. (PS: Some fun bugs are recommended not to be deleted, such as sticking the wall in the wall and hitting people through the wall) I hope this game will get better and better.
